20 Stylish jQuery Image Gallery & Slider Plugins

jQuery is not only a fairly easy javascript language to work with, it is also, when in packaged in a plugin, very easy to install on any web page, making them perfect for non-developers as well. Image galleries/sliders, without the spice of js, tend to be bland and featureless. Throw in a little jQuery and you can have a easily customizable feature-rich image gallery that will present your images professionally and beautifully.

Sideways Fullscreen Image Gallery With jQuery



Galleriffic



Galleria



Awkward Showcase A jQuery Plugin



desSlideshow - Stylish featured image slideshow jQuery plugin



Orbit: A Slick jQuery Image Slider Plugin




YoxView jQuery image viewer plugin

YoxView is a free Lightbox-type media and image viewer jQuery plugin. It's easy to use and feature-rich.



Exposure

Exposure is a jQuery plugin for rich and smart photo viewing that can handle very large amounts of photos. See the Exposure website for more information.



jQuery plugin: jQueryRotate




jQuery Captify




Nivo Jquery Image Slider



Avia Jquery Image Slider



COIN SLIDER jQuery Image Slider with Unique Effects



bxGallery jQuery Image Gallery



slideViewerPro 1.0



Pikachoose



Smooth Div Scroll



Simple Controls Gallery v1.3
